question: 2009 nî choân-nî ê chóng siu-ji̍p sī kúi-tang?
除“總收入”之外，2009年四個季度之間，哪項財務指標保持完全一致？

Tī siánn-ê kuí-tang-á lāi, sán-seng "tuā-tsōo hù-khuán tlāi tsō-siú" ê tsîng-khuán siōng koân? Tī hit ê kuí-tang-á lāi, tū-tī ê "kiat-sûn sòaⁿ m̄-kau-lâi sòaⁿ siáu-tshùn sū-ê siáⁿ-lūi ê iâⁿ-sûn?", tsuí-tuānn-ê siáⁿ-lūi ê iâⁿ-sûn sī siáⁿ-lūi?
2009 ni kin-kuat liam-chham ê chhoat-sū, "siâⁿ-chè hō͘ SL Green chha-bó͘ kó͘-chu thun-chiap hō͘-sún (sún-sit)" ê hêng-thài sī án-choáⁿ-iūⁿ?
answer: Tī 2009 nî ê sî, siâⁿ-chè kó͘-chu ê siâⁿ-chè hō͘-sún choán-ōe chòe keh-chiah ê thun-chiap hêng-thài. Tī 3 goe̍h 31 ê ki-bûn, chū 32,768 ê koân chū-kim khai-sí, kiám-chiok hō͘ 12,543 chiūⁿ 6 goe̍h 30; tō 9 goe̍h 30 thun-chiap ū -2,520, koh tī 12 goe̍h 31 chiap-kīn -5,123 ê sún-sit.

question: Si "net income ( loss ) attributable to sl green" sī tsiàn-tsè ê sî-tsūn, 'gain ( loss ) on sale of discontinued operations' mā sī tsiàn-tsè ê sî, lóng-tsuá ê trimestre sī uîⁿ hâi?

Tī September 30 hō͘ chih-chiap ê kî-kan, "chóng-siāu-siu" ê chē-seng-chiam, "chú-iàu kó͘-pia̍h hō͘-chè" tī liáu chē-chē ê phiah-lī? Chiong si̍t-chāi phiah-lī, tō chē-chām liáu nn̄gê siáu-sià sòa sòa-chhia lâi kiâⁿ.

Nāi-kúi koh-ūi ê 'preferred stock dividends' tōa-la̍t hō͘ siau-tō͘ (tōa-la̍t sī $0) tī September 30 ê kî-kan, hit ê kî-kan ê 'net income ( loss ) attributable to sl green common stockholders' ē-sī siáⁿ-mih?

Koh saⁿ-li̍p ê chu-liāu lâi khòaⁿ, "chháu-chháu choa̍t-tóe hū-chè kim" kap "su̍t-sò͘ sī SL Green kó͘-chá kó͘-chi̍p ê siú-chiok-chiá só͘ tit-tio̍h ê siu-ji̍t (sún-sit)" chi-kan ū sím-mi̍h kiò-chòe iáⁿ-siòng ê koan-hē?
answer: Ū chi̍t ê kiông-sè ê chèng-tòng chha-piah-tō͘. "chháu-chháu choa̍t-tóe hū-chè kim" siōng koân ê nn̄g ê chiap-kî (3 goe̍h 31 hō kap 6 goe̍h 30 hō) mā ū siá--lo̍h-lâi "su̍t-sò͘ sī SL Green kó͘-chá kó͘-chi̍p ê siú-chiok-chiá só͘ tit-tio̍h ê siu-ji̍t (sún-sit)" siōng koân. Keng-chè-á kóng, chiap-kî ê hū-chè koân-té (9 goe̍h 30 hō kap 12 goe̍h 31 hō) hō͘ kó͘-chi̍p ê siú-chiok-chiá chōe-chòe sún-sit, chèng-bêng chiah-ê toā hū-chè sī chi̍t ê tiōng-iàu ê thàu-chúi lâi chōe-chòe siu-ji̍t, te̍k-pia̍t sī tī chi̍t nî ê thâu-cháⁿ pòaⁿ ê sî-chūn.

question: 2009 nî 12 goe̍h 31 ji̍t kàu ê kî-kan, ū kúi hō sêng-pún ê thiàⁿ-chí sī huiⁿ-tāi ê (sún-sit)?

Tī `income ( loss ) net of noncontrolling interests and before gains on sale` chit ê hāng-bo̍k lāi-bīn, hō-chóa ê kî-kan sī tó chi̍t ê, tì-tiāⁿ chāi kî-thaⁿ sann ê kî-kan piáu-hiān chhut bô-kâng ê chhu-sit?
answer: Kî-kan kié-hō͘ Sè-goe̍h 30 sī hit ê chhut-gōa. Kî-thaⁿ sann ê kî-kan lóng tiāⁿ-ài chhú-sūi (`-$380`, `-$10,242`, `-$26,600`), m̄-koh Sè-goe̍h ê kî-kan sī tē it ê lâi chhú-chhúi (`$4,099`), hō͘ i chiâⁿ chòe chi̍t ê te̍k-pia̍t ê hāng-bo̍k.

question: 2009 nî ê kok khuànn ê sì-kùi lāi, siánn-búi ê sì-kùi bôe hōo SL Green teh kò͘-hō͘ ê kó͘-hō͘ siōng chiap-thiam ê siu-ji̍t, hām siánn-búi ê kî-thā hāng-mūi chiap-thiam hōo chit ê kiat-kó?
answer: Kàu 3 goe̍h 31 ji̍t ê sì-kùi bôe hōo SL Green teh kò͘-hō͘ ê kó͘-hō͘ siōng chiap-thiam ê siu-ji̍t sī $32,768. Chit ê siū-ji̍t hōo chē--khah chē ê chóng-siu-ji̍t ($258,787) hām tiâu-chè chha-chhá ê kî-thā chin-kē chha-chhá ê tiāu-siâu sîng-pó ($47,712), chiū-án-ne chiap-hōo ê chha-chhá ê siu-ji̍t ($1,319) chiap-thiam hōo chit ê kiat-kó.
